  completionMessage: Ward seva ab constituency organization ban chuki hai. Reach,
    unity aur readiness ka har number save ho gaya.
  chapterNumber: 9
  nextChapterScene: 
  introTitle: CHAPTER 9 / VIDHANSABHA KI RAAH
  introMessage: Ward ki jeet ko constituency bhar ke accountable public network mein
    badlo.
